Package: BaroWavelet
Type: Package
Title: Baroreflex Sensitivity Assessment with Wavelet Transforms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Alvaro Chao-Ecija <alvarochaoecija.rprojects@gmail.com> [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2691-6936>), 
        Marc Stefan Dawid-Milner [ths]
Maintainer: Alvaro Chao-Ecija <alvarochaoecija.rprojects@gmail.com>
Description: Performs autonomic evaluation and baroreflex sensitivity assessment of interbeat 
             intervals and blood pressure recordings using wavelet transforms. It includes 
             different analysis techniques based on the continuous and discrete wavelet transforms. 
             For more details please check the following in-press article: A Chao-Ecija , 
             MS Dawid-Milner , BaroWavelet: An R-based tool for dynamic baroreflex evaluation 
             through wavelet analysis techniques, Computer Methods and Programs in Biomedicine 
             (2023), <doi:10.1016/j.cmpb.2023.107758>.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
